<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
      font-size: 12pt;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 18pt;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 14pt;
      color: #666;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 12pt;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .party-info {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-left: 4px solid #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .compensation-box {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .benefit-item {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .schedule-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .schedule-table th,
    .schedule-table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .schedule-table th {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .signature-block {
      margin-top: 60px;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
    .signature-line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
      width: 300px;
      height: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .date-line {
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #666;
    }
    .initials-line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #999;
      width: 60px;
      height: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #999;
      border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .notice-box {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>EMPLOYMENT AGREEMENT</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Agreement No: {{contractId}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <p>This Employment Agreement ("Agreement") is entered into as of <strong>{{formatDate effectiveDate}}</strong> (the "Effective Date") by and between:</p>

    <div class="party-info">
      <strong>Employer:</strong><br>
      {{employerName}}<br>
      {{#if employerAddress}}
      Address: {{employerAddress}}<br>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if employerPhone}}
      Phone: {{employerPhone}}
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    <p>and</p>

    <div class="party-info">
      <strong>Employee:</strong><br>
      {{employeeName}}<br>
      {{#if employeeAddress}}
      Address: {{employeeAddress}}<br>
      {{/if}}
      Email: {{employeeEmail}}<br>
      {{#if employeePhone}}
      Phone: {{employeePhone}}
      {{/if}}
      {{#if employeeSSN}}
      SSN: {{employeeSSN}} (for payroll purposes)
      {{/if}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">1. Position and Duties</div>
    <p>The Employer hereby employs the Employee as <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> in the <strong>{{department}}</strong> department. The Employee shall:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Report to: {{reportingManager}}</li>
      <li>Work Location: {{workLocation}}</li>
      <li>Employment Type: {{employmentType}}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>The Employee agrees to perform all duties and responsibilities associated with this position faithfully and to the best of their ability, in accordance with Employer's policies and procedures.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">2. Term of Employment</div>
    <p>This Agreement shall be effective from <strong>{{formatDate effectiveDate}}</strong> and shall continue until terminated in accordance with the provisions of this Agreement.</p>
    {{#if probationPeriodMonths}}
    <div class="notice-box">
      <strong>Probationary Period:</strong> The first {{probationPeriodMonths}} months of employment shall be a probationary period during which either party may terminate with {{probationNoticeDays}} days written notice.
    </div>
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">3. Compensation</div>
    <div class="compensation-box">
      <p><strong>Base Salary:</strong> {{baseSalary}} per {{payFrequency}}</p>
      <p><strong>Annualized:</strong> {{annualizedSalary}}</p>
      {{#if signingBonus}}
      <p><strong>Signing Bonus:</strong> {{signingBonus}} (payable upon satisfactory completion of probation)</p>
      {{/if}}
      <p>Salary shall be paid {{payFrequency}} in accordance with Employer's standard payroll practices.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">4. Bonus and Incentive Programs</div>
    {{#if hasBonusProgram}}
    <p>The Employee may be eligible for the following bonus programs:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Annual Performance Bonus:</strong> Up to {{annualBonusPercent}}% of base salary based on individual and company performance</li>
      {{#if stiPercent}}
      <li><strong>Short-Term Incentive:</strong> {{stiPercent}}% of base salary</li>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if ltiGrant}}
      <li><strong>Long-Term Incentive:</strong> {{ltiGrant}} stock options/RSUs (vesting over {{vestingPeriod}})</li>
      {{/if}}
    </ul>
    <p>Bonus eligibility and amounts are at the sole discretion of the Employer and subject to change.</p>
    {{else}}
    <p>No bonus programs are currently applicable to this position.</p>
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">5. Benefits</div>
    <p>The Employee shall be entitled to participate in the following benefit programs (subject to eligibility requirements):</p>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <strong>Health Insurance:</strong> {{healthPlanType}} - Coverage begins {{healthCoverageStart}}
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <strong>Paid Time Off:</strong> {{ptoDays}} days per year
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <strong>Sick Leave:</strong> {{sickLeaveDays}} days per year
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <strong>Holidays:</strong> {{holidayCount}} paid holidays per year
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <strong>Retirement Plan:</strong> {{retirementPlan}} - Employer match up to {{employerMatchPercent}}
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <strong>Life Insurance:</strong> {{lifeInsuranceAmount}} coverage (2x base salary)
    </div>
    {{#if hasStockPurchase}}
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <strong>Employee Stock Purchase Plan (ESPP):</strong> Available after {{esppEligibilityMonths}} months
    </div>
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">6. Work Schedule</div>
    <p>The Employee's regular work schedule shall be:</p>
    <table class="schedule-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Day</th>
          <th>Start Time</th>
          <th>End Time</th>
          <th>Break</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Monday</td>
          <td>{{mondayStart}}</td>
          <td>{{mondayEnd}}</td>
          <td>{{mondayBreak}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Tuesday</td>
          <td>{{tuesdayStart}}</td>
          <td>{{tuesdayEnd}}</td>
          <td>{{tuesdayBreak}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Wednesday</td>
          <td>{{wednesdayStart}}</td>
          <td>{{wednesdayEnd}}</td>
          <td>{{wednesdayBreak}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Thursday</td>
          <td>{{thursdayStart}}</td>
          <td>{{thursdayEnd}}</td>
          <td>{{thursdayBreak}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Friday</td>
          <td>{{fridayStart}}</td>
          <td>{{fridayEnd}}</td>
          <td>{{fridayBreak}}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    {{#if remoteWorkAllowed}}
    <p><strong>Remote Work:</strong> {{remoteWorkPolicy}}</p>
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">7. Confidentiality and Intellectual Property</div>
    <p>The Employee agrees to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Maintain strict confidentiality of all proprietary information, trade secrets, and business data</li>
      <li>Assign to the Employer all inventions, developments, and works of authorship created during employment</li>
      <li>Comply with all confidentiality and non-disclosure agreements</li>
      <li>Return all company property and confidential information upon termination</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">8. Non-Compete and Non-Solicitation</div>
    {{#if hasNonCompete}}
    <p>During employment and for {{nonCompetePeriod}} months following termination, the Employee shall not:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Work for any competitor in a similar capacity</li>
      <li>Solicit Employer's customers or clients</li>
      <li>Solicit Employer's employees for employment</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Geographic Scope:</strong> {{nonCompeteScope}}</p>
    {{else}}
    <p>No non-compete restrictions apply to this position.</p>
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">9. Termination</div>
    <p><strong>By Employer:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>For Cause: Immediate termination without notice</li>
      <li>Without Cause: {{employerNoticePeriod}} weeks notice or payment in lieu of notice</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>By Employee:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>{{employeeNoticePeriod}} weeks written notice required</li>
    </ul>
    {{#if severancePackage}}
    <p><strong>Severance Package:</strong> {{severancePackage}}</p>
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">10. General Provisions</div>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Governing Law:</strong> This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of {{governingLaw}}</li>
      <li><strong>Entire Agreement:</strong> This Agreement constitutes the entire employment agreement</li>
      <li><strong>Amendments:</strong> Modifications must be in writing and signed by both parties</li>
      <li><strong>Severability:</strong> Invalid provisions shall not affect remaining provisions</li>
      <li><strong>Waiver:</strong> Failure to enforce shall not constitute a waiver</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="signature-block">
    <p><strong>IN WITNESS WHEREOF</strong>, the parties have executed this Agreement as of the date first written above.</p>

    <table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 30px;">
      <tr>
        <td style="width: 50%; padding-right: 20px;">
          <strong>EMPLOYER:</strong><br><br>
          {{employerName}}<br><br>
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p>Authorized Signature</p>
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p>Print Name & Title</p>
          <p class="date-line">Date: _______________</p>
        </td>
        <td style="width: 50%; padding-left: 20px;">
          <strong>EMPLOYEE:</strong><br><br>
          {{employeeName}}<br><br>
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p>Employee Signature</p>
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p>Print Name</p>
          <p class="date-line">Date: _______________</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>ACKNOWLEDGMENT:</strong></p>
    <p>I acknowledge that I have received, read, and understand this Employment Agreement. I agree to comply with all terms and conditions set forth herein.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
      Employee Initials: <span class="initials-line"></span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Generated on {{generatedDateFormatted}} by REZ Contract Management System</p>
    <p>Contract ID: {{contractId}}</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
